    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i've seen so many articles about how they're working on \"ambient sensing\" and using wifi signals or tiny fluctuations in electricity to detect movement and even breathing patterns. if they can do that, wouldnt it be a small step to correlate that data with the smart devices i already have in my house? it just seems like they have all the pieces for it.",
